reviewText: Just as funny as series 1 and 2.  My only complaint is that they end too soon.  :)  The usual cast of character is still here and it's still brilliantly done.  If you are a fan if British comedy--surreal British comedy especially--I highly recommend this show.  The cast is great, and the writing is excellent.  Steven Toast continues his acting and um, personal, exploits as only he can!
